{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63af88bc1b","title":"和苏修大使契尔沃年科的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a7f914eca6","index":0,"year":1963,"month":2,"day":23,"articleId":"63af88bc1b"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"12b3545cfe","type":"title","text":"和苏修大使契尔沃年科的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"},{"id":"a97e254bdb","type":"paragraph","text":"（苏修大使契尔沃年科求见毛泽东，毛泽东称不适。因再三要求，毛泽东着睡衣接见。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"},{"id":"393a52dd53","type":"paragraph","text":"契：听说你们要发表文章，不必要的，感到很沉重。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"},{"id":"1ee2ddd386","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不必要，你们为什么发表那么多文章？没有什么沉重的，不过互相论战，不过是唇枪舌剑而已","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"},{"id":"b66ab79ea3","type":"paragraph","text":"奖：请你到莫斯科去谈一谈，可以吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"},{"id":"f2295ba164","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我已经老了，不中用了。老而不死，破套鞋去不成了。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b"}],"page":{"id":"f31909d8a2","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"63af88bc1b","start":360,"end":360}}}},"__N_SSG":true}